      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-representative hardware. Testing split across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH biomechanics lab and DePuy Synthes R&D lab) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Sample size supports computation of validation uncertainty metric uval."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
