      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5 for each QoI: stiffness 1.31, yield force 1.54, force at 40 mm 1.78. All values below 1.96 threshold. Mean absolute percent differences: 4.8%, 6.2%, 7.1% respectively, all within pre-specified 10% acceptance bound."
    },
