      "rationale": "Construct stiffness governs load sharing with the vertebral column; yield force and force at 40 mm displacement are the primary ASTM F1717 acceptance metrics used in 510(k) submissions. QoI selection reviewed and approved by FDA CDRH reviewer team. Traceability matrix documented."
